## Lab Oval Diamond Prices by Carat — Full Dataset

### 1.5ct Lab Oval Diamonds

The 1.5ct tier is the entry point for lab oval diamonds on Blue Nile, and it is remarkably uniform in price. At $2,935, the IGI D-IF/FL Ideal Cut lab oval is the best-value entry in the entire fancy-shape lab market. For comparison, the cheapest natural oval at 1.5ct is an [E-VS2 GIA at $8,757](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28918376?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — a stone two full color grades below and three clarity grades below what the lab delivers at $2,935.

